    "title": "Prettify the page with an image (step 4 of 9)",
    "url": "https://openxt.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ds/pages/294915/Prettify+the+page+with+an+image+(step+4+of+9)",
    "content": "<p>Owned by Anonymous\nLast updated: Jul 27, 2014 by Anonymous\n\n</p><div class=\"contentLayout\" data-atlassian-layout='{\"name\":\"pagelayout-two-right\",\"columns\":[\"large\",\"aside\"],\"header\":true,\"footer\":true}'><div class=\"header\"><div class=\"innerCell\"><p style=\"margin-left: 60.0px;\"> </p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\">The Confluence editor has been built to create content, fast. But that doesn't just mean using the written word, creating lists, or inserting links. <br/></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\">You can embed images, Office documents, and videos – and that is just the tip of the iceberg when it comes to creating useful content for your teammates. <br/> </span></p></div></div><div class=\"columnLayout twoColumns\"><div class=\"cell large\"><div class=\"innerCell\"><ol><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Edit</strong> the page.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Click in the right-hand column to position your cursor.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Click the <strong>Insert</strong> button in the editor toolbar. It looks like this:<br/><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"step04-00.jpg\"></ri:attachment></ac:image><br/><br/></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Choose <strong>Image</strong> to launch the 'Insert Image' dialog.<br/><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"step04-01.jpg\"></ri:attachment></ac:image><br/><br/></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>The 'Attached Images' tab shows you the images attached to this page. <br/>Click the image named <strong>Confluence Origami Necktie</strong>.<br/></span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Click <strong>Insert</strong>.</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\">You will return to this page, and see the 'Image Properties Panel'. If you don't see it, click the image.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\">You can resize the image by clicking on the square buttons.<br/><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"step04-02.jpg\"></ri:attachment></ac:image> <br/></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\"><br/></span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\">Click <strong>Effects</strong> and then select the <strong>Curl Shadow</strong> option from the 'Image Effects' dialog. <br/><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"step04-03.jpg\"></ri:attachment></ac:image> <br/> </span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\">Your image should look like this when completed:<br/><ac:image ac:queryparams=\"effects=border-simple,shadow-kn\" ac:thumbnail=\"true\" ac:width=\"300\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Confluence-Origami-Necktie.jpeg\"></ri:attachment></ac:image><br/> </span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Click <strong>Save</strong> to save the page.<br/><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"step04-04.jpg\"></ri:attachment></ac:image></li></ol></div></div><div class=\"cell aside\"><div class=\"innerCell\"><p> </p></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><div class=\"innerCell\"><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\"><br/></span></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\"><ac:link><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Let's edit this page (step 3 of 9)\"></ri:page><ac:link-body><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"prev.jpg\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Let's edit this page (step 3 of 9)\"></ri:page></ri:attachment></ac:image></ac:link-body></ac:link> <ac:link><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Welcome to Confluence\"></ri:page><ac:link-body><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"home.jpg\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Let's edit this page (step 3 of 9)\"></ri:page></ri:attachment></ac:image></ac:link-body></ac:link> <ac:link><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Get serious with a table (step 5 of 9)\"></ri:page><ac:link-body><ac:image><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"next.jpg\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Let's edit this page (step 3 of 9)\"></ri:page></ri:attachment></ac:image></ac:link-body></ac:link></span></h1><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);\"><br/></span></p></div></div></div>",
